         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ Hamburg, ¶  ¶ 11 July ¶  ¶ 55 ¶ Esteemed ¶  ¶ Professor, ¶  ¶  ¶ Dr Mueller has sent me the ¶  ¶ enclosed ¶  ¶ two printed ¶  ¶ items ¶  ¶ for you, which I ¶  ¶ send on ¶  ¶ to you herewith. The go...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M55.07.11a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">MS not seen; text given here extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">27</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Hamburg d. 11 Juli<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>55</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrter Herr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Herr Dr. Müller hat mir die beifolgenden beiden Drucksachen für Sie gesandt, die ich Ihnen hiermit zustelle. Der gute Freund wäre kürzlich bald in Folge einer Erkältung die er sich beim Suchen von Wasserpflanzen zuzog, gestorben. Nachher hätte er bald seine Stelle verloren, da alle Deutschen missliebig wurden, weil ein Hannoveraner an der Spitze der Revolution stand. Er hat aber dies Missgeschick auch überstanden und so hoffe ich, dass es ihm auch ferner gut ergehen werde.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Den ersten Report über seine Reisen hat Müller unvorsichtigerweise einem nach Europa reisenden Kaufmann mitgegeben, der ihn aber nicht abgeliefert hat, es thut mir leid, dass auch ein für Sie bestimmtes Exemplar dabei war.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bin wohl für die beiden Hefte der Linnaea bei Ihnen in der Schuld, will diese aber erst noch vergrössern, bevor ich die abtrage. Dr. Müller schreibt mir, er wünsche den<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">ganzen</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Jahrgang der Linnaea von 1853 bis 1854 zu erhalten. Von Band X habe ich Heft IV u V liegen, möchten Sie die Güte haben u mir das Uebrige davon zuschicken u dann den Preis anzugeben, den ich Ihnen bald zustellen werde. Wenn es angeht, wäre es mir lieb, die Hefte bis zum 20 oder 21 d. M. hier zu haben, da ich am 22 eine Kiste für Dr. Müller abschicke.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich füge ein wenig Abfall aus der letzten Kiste bei;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ausserdem erlaube ich mir ein Buch für Herrn Schmidt beizulegen. Nächstens werde ich Ihnen auch wieder etwas Manuskript zuschicken, die Xerotideen etc habe ich fertig. Wenn die anderen Arbeiter an den Pl. Müll. nur fleissiger wären. Für die Hefte über die Bentham’schen Mimoseen danke verbindlichst.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochachtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebenster</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Hamburg,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>11 July<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>55</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Dr Mueller has sent me the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>enclosed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>two printed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>items<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for you, which I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>send on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to you herewith. The good friend would soon have died recently as a result of a cold he<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>caught while looking for water plants. Afterwards<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he would soon have lost his position, as all Germans were<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>unpopular<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>because a Hanoverian was at the head of the revolution.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Eureka rebellion. The Hanoverian leader was Friedrich Wern.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>See Wehner (2017), pp. 51-5.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The threat to M's position<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had little if anything to do with the rebellion but<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was financial, with major cut-backs proposed in government<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>expenditure, including its various scientific services.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>However, he<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has also<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>survived this misfortune and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>so<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I hope that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>henceforth<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he will<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>even<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>fare well.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>—<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>incautiously<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>gave the first report on his travels to a merchant travelling to Europe, but he<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not delivered<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>it; I'm sorry that a copy intended for you was also included.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am probably in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>debt to you for the two parts<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Linnaea</seg>, but I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>will add to it first before I repay it. Dr Mueller writes me that he would like to receive the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">entire</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>volume of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Linnaea</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from 1853 to 1854. I have<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>parts<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>IV and V of volume X. Would you be so kind as to send me the rest of them and then let me know the price, which I will send you soon. If it is possible, I would appreciate it if you could have the issues here by the 20th or 21st of this month, because I am sending off a box for Dr Mueller on the 22nd.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am enclosing a little<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>waste from the last crate;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in addition<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am also taking the liberty of enclosing a book for Mr Schmidt. Next I will also send you some manuscript again, I have the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Xerotideae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>etc. ready. If only the other workers on the Plantae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Muellerianae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>were more industrious. Thank you very much for the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>parts<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on Bentham's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mimoseae.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Most devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
         </div>
      </body>
